data.description: Located in the heart of McMinnville, we have a cute 2BR/1BA cottage just waiting for you to make it your home.  This cozy charmer has hardwood flooring in the living room, hall, and both bedrooms. There is also a 6' wood privacy fence enclosing the entire backyard, which is perfect for entertaining and allowing your pets to explore and play, worry free. The HVAC, roof, water heater, cabinets, and 6' wooden privacy fence are all less than 6 years old.  All appliances, including the washer and dryer, will stay with the property.  Call today for your private showing because this one will not be on the market long.
